import { useDispatch, useSelector } from "react-redux"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import { clearCart, addToCart, decreaseCart, removeFromCart } from "../features/cartSlice"; const Cart = () => { const cart = useSelector((state) => state.cart); const dispatch = useDispatch(); const handleRemoveFromCart = (cartItem) => { dispatch(removeFromCart(cartItem)); }; const handleDecreaseCart = (cartItem) => { dispatch(decreaseCart(cartItem)) }; const handleIncreaseCart = (cartItem) => { dispatch(addToCart(cartItem)) }; const handleClearCart = () => { dispatch(clearCart()); }; return (

Shopping Cart

{ cart.cartItems.length === 0 ? (

Your cart is currently empty

Start Shopping
) : (

Product

Price

Quantity

Total

{cart.cartItems?.map(cartItem => (

{cartItem.name}

{cartItem.desc}

${cartItem.price}
{cartItem.cartQuantity}
${cartItem.price * cartItem.cartQuantity}
))}
Subtotal ${cart.cartTotalAmount}

Taxes and Shipping Calculated at Checkout

Continue Shopping
)}
) }; export default Cart;
